expression = re.compile(rfc._ASCTIME_DATETIME_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['Mon, 31 Oct 1982 03:21:45 GMT',
    'Thu, 01 Feb 2045 20:34:22 GMT', 'Monday, 31-Oct-82 03:21:45 GMT',
    'Thursday, 01-Feb-45 20:34:22 GMT', 'Something else']
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad asctime datetime '{d}' matched regex".format(d=bad_example))
